{"tid":280333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家OK賣緊果隻debit卡好搵笨, 要小心","createTime":"2017-06-12T04:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T06:17:48.000Z","uid":1295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b8e0f77b391493cbe2bb98a0de07980c2f99427","tid":280333,"uid":1295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:09:34.000Z","msg":"之前係OK有隻由33金融出既debit卡, 一年前買咗張500蚊, 見卡面寫住19年先到期諗住慢慢用, 前幾日想拿出黎用用唔到, 仲比佢扣咗50 mgt fee, <br />\n打去客服問, 佢話卡有效期只係由購買日起計12個月, 卡面果個係參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過咗期卡會失效, 仲會每月扣50, 要攞返餘額要比80蚊手續費加等2個月發支票比你<br />\n<br />\n張卡500買返黎實得370, 真係好做過大耳窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位有興趣的巴打真係要小心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.33finance.com/wp-content/themes/versus-wp/layout/images/373/Cards3_V2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.33finance.com%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fversus-wp%2Flayout%2Fimages%2F373%2FCards3_V2.jpg&h=3410188e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32bea93c62fdde42b5d89fc0c75fc7725d950d9e","tid":280333,"uid":55922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"用依張不如用 Tap &amp; Go <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865492061ba2fe2a600bc9623bd9ec9f7f9d84e2","tid":280333,"uid":1295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用依張不如用 Tap &amp; Go <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係，佢又唔可以增值，只可話用黎送禮啱用"},{"pid":"dcc3e509c738f4a45b017ea81ae0873894a6c7b0","tid":280333,"uid":13645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"張卡不記名<br />\n用黎買正版4 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}